# Icons (Tabler)

This project uses **Tabler Icons** (`@tabler/icons-react`). Never import from `lucide-react`, `react-icons`, `@heroicons/react`, or other icon libraries.

- **Import from `@tabler/icons-react`.** Tabler names use an `Icon` prefix: `IconPlus`, `IconArrowLeft`, `IconTrash`.
- **Icons in `Button` use `data-icon`.** `data-icon="inline-start"` (prefix) or `data-icon="inline-end"` (suffix). No `mr-2`, `size-4`, or other sizing/spacing classes on the icon.
- **Pass icons as component objects, not string keys.** `icon={IconCheck}`, not a string lookup map.
- **Registry components may ship with Lucide imports.** Swap them to the matching Tabler icon when adding shadcn components.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — wrong library
import { Plus } from "lucide-react";

// ❌ BAD — manual spacing/sizing in a Button
<Button>
  <IconPlus className="mr-2 size-4" />
  Add issue
</Button>

// ✅ GOOD
import { IconPlus } from "@tabler/icons-react";

<Button>
  <IconPlus data-icon="inline-start" />
  Add issue
</Button>
```
